COVID-19 Public Health Status by County from ESRI

Source: R/pub_hlth_status_by_cnty.R
pub_hlth_status_by_cnty.Rd

This functions pulls the public health status by county in the US as of the current date. The data comes from ESRI open data website. The data is 1 row per county.

pub_hlth_status_by_cnty()

Value

A dataframe/tibble

Details

Website: https://coronavirus-disasterresponse.hub.arcgis.com/datasets/97792521be744711a291d10ecef33a61/data?geometry=76.921

Examples

pub_status_cnty <- R.COVID.19::pub_hlth_status_by_cnty()
